Titolo: Ninja Crusaders

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: Ninja Crusaders is a side-scrolling action game released by Sammy for the Nintendo Entertainment System in 1990. The player takes control of one of two ninjas who are tasked at thwarting an alien invasion. The game has been compared to Tecmo's Ninja Gaiden series.

Genere: 2D action 

Valutazione: N/A
